Description: Casanode - dVPN node management via Bluetooth and TCP API
  Casanode is a lightweight service for managing decentralized VPN (dVPN) nodes.
  It enables secure communication via Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) and a RESTful
  TCP API, allowing monitoring, configuration, and lifecycle control. The service
  includes Docker support and SSL authentication for secure node operations.
